BioShock 2 provides players with the perfect blend of explosive

storytelling. The halls of Rapture once again echo with sins of the

Rapture. Players step into the boots of the most iconic denizen of
Rapture, the Big Daddy, as they travel through the decrepit and
beautiful fallen city, chasing an unseen foe in search of answers
and their own survival
